 🧠 AI Research Paper Summarizer & Insight Extraction

✨ About This Project
Reading research papers can be overwhelming — long texts, complex ideas, and too much information to process quickly.  

This project aims to simplify that experience by building an **AI-powered research assistant** that can automatically:
- Summarize research papers  
- Extract meaningful insights  
- Help users understand key ideas faster  

It combines modern NLP techniques with intelligent retrieval systems to make academic reading more efficient and accessible.

---

🚀 What Makes This Project Special?
Instead of just summarizing text, this system goes a step further:

🔍 Understands context using advanced AI models  
📄 Generates concise and meaningful summaries  
🧠 Extracts key insights, not just sentences  
🔗 Connects information using a knowledge graph  
⚡ Uses Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) for better accuracy  

---

## 🏗️ How It Works (Simple Flow)
Research Papers → Processing → Embeddings → Vector Search → AI Model → Insights & Summary



